##construir os histogramas pra todas as variaveis

nomes_vari<-dados |> select(amg:v) |> names()
for(i in seq_along(nomes_vari)){
plot_hist<-dados |>
  ggplot(aes_string(x=nomes_vari[i])) +
  geom_histogram(
    bins=10,
    color="black",
    fill="lightgray"
  )+
  theme_minimal()
print(plot_hist)
}

library(DT)
dados |> 
  datatable()

#Grfico de Barras de Erros

Agrupar os dados por superficies, criar o resumo com mdia e desvio padrao para os dados de argila

dados |> 
  group_by(sup) |> 
  summarise(
    media=mean(argila),
    desvpad=sd(argila),
    epm=desvpad/sqrt(n())
  ) |> 
  ggplot(aes(x=sup,y=media))+
  geom_col(
    color="black",
    fill="lightgray"
    )+
  geom_errorbar(
    aes(
      ymax=media+epm,
      ymin=media-epm),
                color="red",
                width=0.25,)+
    # Ajuste esttico do tema
  theme_minimal(base_size = 12) +
  theme(
    plot.title = element_text(hjust = 0.5, face = "bold"),
    plot.subtitle = element_text(hjust = 0.5),
    panel.grid.major = element_line(color = "gray85"),
    panel.grid.minor = element_blank(),
  )

library(dplyr)
library(ggplot2)
library(viridis)

dados |> 
  group_by(sup) |>
  summarise(
    media = mean(argila),
    desvpad = sd(argila),
    epm = desvpad / sqrt(n())
  ) |>
  ggplot(aes(x = sup, y = media, fill = sup)) +
  # Barras
  geom_col(
    color = "darkgray",
    width = 0.7
  ) +
  # Barras de erro
  geom_errorbar(
    aes(ymax = media + epm, ymin = media - epm),
    color = "gray20",
    width = 0.25
  ) +
  # Ttulos e rtulos
  labs(
    title = "Mdia de Argila por Categoria",
    subtitle = "Barras de erro representam o Erro Padro da Mdia (EPM)",
    x = NULL,
    y = "Mdia de Argila (%)",
    fill = "Sup"
  ) +
  # Paleta de cores suave
  scale_fill_manual(values = c("#4D4D4D", "#A6A6A6", "#E0E0E0")) +
  # Ajustes do tema
  theme_minimal(base_size = 12, base_family = "Times New Roman") +
  theme(
    plot.title = element_text(hjust = 0.5, face = "bold"),
    plot.subtitle = element_text(color="gray20",
                                 hjust = 0.5),
    panel.grid.major = element_line(color = "gray85"),
    panel.grid.minor = element_blank(),
    panel.border = element_rect(color = "darkgray", fill = NA, size = 0.7),
    panel.background = element_rect(fill = "white", color = NA),
    plot.background = element_rect(fill = "white", color = NA),
    legend.position = c(0.90, 0.80),
    legend.background = element_rect(fill = alpha("white", 0.8), color = "darkgray"),
    legend.key = element_blank(),
    legend.title = element_text(
      face = "bold",
      color="gray20")
  )
